                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18211205-93-victim1089 t18211205-93-viclabel577"></join>, and live in Green Man's-row, Bethnal-green. I left these things in a box, at my brothers; I afterwards went, and found it broken open, and the things gone.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18211205-93-person1091">
                  WILLIAM 
                  HESSE
               <interp inst="t18211205-93-person1091" type="surname" value="HESSE"></interp>
